     <div class="column23"> 
      <h3>RESOURCES FOR FINDING EMPLOYMENT</h3> 
      <p>Academic Employment opportunities at UCR may be located on the employment pages for our colleges and schools. In addition, beginning in the 2013-2014 Academic Year, select employment opportunities may be located via the campus’ Academic Personnel Recruitment System. Please visit the links below to assist you with finding academic employment opportunities.</p> 
      <a id="expand-all" style="text-decoration: none; float: right;" onclick="xpandall()" href="#xpander">Expand All</a> 
      <br> 
      <div class="boxA"> 
       <h5>ACADEMIC EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITIES AT UCR</h5> 
       <div class="xpander"> 
        <ul> 
         <li><a href="https://aprecruit.ucr.edu/" target="_blank">AP Recruit Online Recruitment System</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://www.engr.ucr.edu/employment.html" target="_blank">Bourns College of Engineering</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://chass.ucr.edu/employment.html" target="_blank">College of Humanities, Arts, and Social Sciences</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://cnas.ucr.edu/faculty/openings.html" target="_blank">College of Natural and Agricultural Sciences</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://education.ucr.edu/jobs.html" target="_blank">Graduate School of Education</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://library.ucr.edu/employment/" target="_blank">Library</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://soba.ucr.edu/employment/" target="_blank">School of Business Administration</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://medschool.ucr.edu/employment/" target="_blank">School of Medicine and Biomedical Sciences Division</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://www.extension.ucr.edu/" target="_blank">University Extension</a></li> 
        </ul> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="boxB"> 
       <h5>STAFF EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITIES AT UCR</h5> 
       <div class="xpander"> 
        <ul> 
         <li><a href="http://hr.ucr.edu/" target="_blank">UCR Human Resources Job Sites</a></li> 
        </ul> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="boxD"> 
       <h5>HIGHER EDUCATION RECRUITMENT CONSORTIUM</h5> 
       <div class="xpander"> 
        <p>The University of California, Riverside is a proud founding member of the Southern California Higher Education Recruitment Consortium. Visit <a href="http://www.hercjobs.org/southern_california" target="_blank">www.hercjobs.org/southern_california</a> for academic and staff employment opportunities at colleges and universities located throughout Southern California.</p> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <p>In accordance with Federal law, we are making available our <a href="http://police.ucr.edu/clery/clery.html" target="_blank">Campus Security Report</a> to all prospective employees upon request.</p> 
     </div> 
